\fs24\fc0\cf0 When you make a suggestion, the first player to your left who holds any of the cards named in your suggestion must reveal one of these cards to disprove your suggestion.  In this way, you can learn which players hold which cards, and which cards are not held by any players -- these cards are the ones which represent the final solution to the murder.\
