\b\fc1\cf1 Disproving a Suggestion\

\b0\fs8 \

\fs24\fc0\cf0 If an opponent makes a suggestion that includes one or more cards you were dealt, and no other player has disproved the suggestion before you, then you must reveal one of these cards to disprove the suggestion.\
